(Subtask 1: Image Classification) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Introduction) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The first subtask is a supervised image-vector classification problem. Each image is represented) Tj
T*
( as a 256-dimensional vector, and the goal is to predict one of ten class labels for unseen test) Tj
T*
( samples.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The baseline is Softmax Regression. I use a nonlinear ensemble that is still fully OJ-compliant:) Tj
T*
( the submitted Classifier reads the judge-provided training pickle files, trains in ) Tj
T*
(Classifier.__init__, and stores no pretrained sidecar weights. The implementation also includes ) Tj
T*
(a soft time guard so that, on a slower judge machine, it can stop adding ensemble members and ) Tj
T*
(still return predictions from the best model set trained so far.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Methodology) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Inputs are standardized by training-set statistics:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(tilde{x}_i = frac{x_i-mu_i}{sigma_i}.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Because the 256 features are flattened \(16times16\) grayscale images, I use one-pixel shift ) Tj
T*
(augmentation. The training set is expanded by the original image and four cardinal shifts:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(mathcal{T}={\(0,0\),\(-1,0\),\(1,0\),\(0,-1\),\(0,1\)}.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For every transformed image, each neural member computes) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(h^{\(l\)}=max\(0,h^{\(l-1\)}W^{\(l\)}+b^{\(l\)}\),) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(followed by a softmax probability vector \(p_m\(x\)\). The submitted ensemble uses three MLPs plus a) Tj
T*
( low-weight gradient-boosting diversity member:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Member | Configuration | Weight) Tj
T*
(MLP | \(384, 192\), seed 123 | 1.00) Tj
T*
(MLP | \(256, 128\), seed 456 | 1.00) Tj
T*
(MLP | \(512,\), seed 789 | 1.00) Tj
T*
(HistGradientBoosting | 200 iterations, seed 2026 | 0.25) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(At inference time, the same shift set is used as test-time augmentation \(TTA\). The final score ) Tj
T*
(is) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(s_c\(x\)=sum_{tinmathcal{T}}sum_m w_m p_{m,c}\(t\(x\)\),qquad) Tj
T*
(hat{y}=argmax_c s_c\(x\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Pseudo-code:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(  load classification_train_data.pkl and classification_train_label.pkl) Tj
T*
(  fit a StandardScaler on raw training features) Tj
T*
(  augment the training set with 4 cardinal one-pixel shifts) Tj
T*
(  set a soft deadline below the 600 second task limit) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
