(  for each planned ensemble member:) Tj
T*
(      train the member if the remaining time is sufficient) Tj
T*
(      otherwise stop and keep the members trained so far) Tj
T*
(  for inference:) Tj
T*
(      for each TTA shift:) Tj
T*
(          standardize shifted query features) Tj
T*
(          accumulate weighted predict_proba outputs) Tj
T*
