T*
() Tj
T*
(The code avoids pickle model artifacts and remains under the 600 second per-task limit in local ) Tj
T*
(simulation. On the current validation machine, all planned members finish training before the ) Tj
T*
(guard activates.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3. Experiments) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(I used a stratified 80/20 validation split with random seed 123. The local softmax-style ) Tj
T*
(baseline is sklearn Logistic Regression on standardized features.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Model | Validation Accuracy) Tj
T*
(Logistic Regression proxy baseline | 0.5062) Tj
T*
(MLP \(384,192\) with 5-shift TTA | 0.5712) Tj
T*
(MLP \(256,128\) with 5-shift TTA | 0.5689) Tj
T*
(MLP \(512,\) with 5-shift TTA | 0.5634) Tj
T*
(Submitted MLP + HGB probability ensemble | 0.5926) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(I also tested adding more MLPs and a 9-shift augmentation/TTA variant. The final version keeps ) Tj
T*
(the low-weight HGB member because it gives a small but consistent diversity gain while remaining) Tj
T*
( inside the 600 second limit under the time guard.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Subtask 2: Image Retrieval) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. Introduction) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The second subtask is image retrieval. Given a query feature vector, the model must return five ) Tj
T*
(repository rows that are considered similar. The updated Q&A clarified that the output should be) Tj
T*
( repository row indices, not image IDs.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The baseline is raw Euclidean nearest-neighbor search. Since no official relevance labels are ) Tj
T*
(provided, I optimize observable robustness proxies while preserving strong raw-neighbor ) Tj
T*
(behavior.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2. Methodology) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The submitted method combines semantic reranking, standardized-distance fallback, exact self-) Tj
T*
(query handling, and transform-aware replacement. During Retrieval.__init__, the code reads the ) Tj
T*
(judge-provided classification training data if available, maps repository image IDs to labels, ) Tj
T*
(and trains a soft-vote semantic classifier:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Member | Input | Weight) Tj
T*
(HistGradientBoostingClassifier, 220 iterations | raw features | 0.10) Tj
T*
(HistGradientBoostingClassifier, 350 iterations | raw features | 0.20) Tj
T*
(MLPClassifier \(256,\) | standardized features | 0.10) Tj
T*
(MLPClassifier \(512,\) | standardized features | 0.20) Tj
T*
(ExtraTreesClassifier, 500 trees | raw features | 0.40) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For each query, the semantic ensemble predicts a class distribution. Raw Euclidean distance ) Tj
T*
(forms the nearest 200 repository candidates, and the final top-5 first prefers the nearest ) Tj
T*
ET
endstream
